visual.name: EmeraldBI-GanttView
visual.description: The BI-GanttView Charts allow for easier and faster communication of key milestones to the project sponsors and tasks to the responsible team members, with strong grouping and coloring capabilities. Extended data elements and baseline comparisons make BI-GanttView a critical communication tool for your project team.
